# --- Puzzle 5: The Jammed Clock ---

on "fix clock" in [clock_tower_base] {
  require has_item(wrench)
  effect set_flag(clock_fixed)
  effect spawn_item(founders_journal_page_1, clock_tower_base)
  effect solve_puzzle(clock_tower_mechanism)
  effect add_score(15)
  success "You fit the wrench over the misaligned gear and heave. Metal screams against metal — then catches. The gear clicks into place, and the mechanism shudders to life. The clock's hands begin to move for the first time in years. As it chimes, a hidden panel in the clock base springs open, revealing a folded journal page."
