  success "'Together, Malfoy. The Stone is bigger than either of us.' Draco stares at you for a long moment. Something shifts behind his eyes — not warmth, exactly, but the absence of hostility. 'Fine. But when this is over, we go back to hating each other.' He almost smiles. 'Deal?' You nod. An alliance forged in the place that values cunning above all. Somehow, it fits."
  fail "Draco isn't here, or your earlier actions have made alliance impossible."
  done "You and Draco have already reached an understanding."
  once
}

